      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUMMER SPRITZ (7) hit the ground running off the low draw last start and was never headed (22.89) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Ideally placed to take this out. ARCHIE'S GIFT (6) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (24.91) in a Grade 5 at Bendigo. Solid record here winning three races. Key player if finds best. ASTON RECORD (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Paw Hazeldon (23.15) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Hard to beat again. ASTON RYAN (3) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
